01:36.304 --> 01:37.722
Do you have a boyfriend or?

01:39.224 --> 01:41.851
Um, no. No, I'm--

01:42.435 --> 01:43.978
- Mm-mm, no.
Well, I should warn you,

01:43.978 --> 01:45.855
