<i>♪ I don't mind ♪</i>

04:33.648 --> 04:35.108
<i>♪ I don't mind ♪</i>

04:35.108 --> 04:38.319
<i>♪ That I won't buy
that perfect gift ♪</i>

04:38.319 --> 04:44.492
<i>♪ Based on something
I remembered you once said ♪</i>

04:45.034 --> 04:47.870
<i>♪ Come to thiiink ♪</i>

04:47.870 --> 04:51.249
<i>♪ It gives my soul
