to return it ♪</i>

04:54.669 --> 04:58.006
<i>♪ 'Cause I never plan ahead ♪</i>

04:58.006 --> 05:01.259
<i>♪ And as Santa Cons
are drinking ♪</i>

05:01.259 --> 05:04.846
<i>♪ I still wonder what
