05:19.319 --> 05:24.407
<i>♪ So, I really hope
that yours sucks ♪</i>

05:25.116 --> 05:28.745
<i>♪ Mooore ♪</i>

05:35.543 --> 05:37.003
<i>Ooh, and another thing,</i>

05:37.003 --> 05:38.713
<i>Donner's antlers have
got four points...</i>

05:38.713 --> 05:41.341
