Book. Good job.

06:20.546 --> 06:25.676
<i>The Unlikely Adventure
of Squid the Squirrel.</i>

06:25.676 --> 06:28.930
Y-You told me to send it
to you when I was finished, so.

06:30.640 --> 06:32.433
I had a feeling about you.

06:32.433 --> 06:33.976
You, you liked it?

06:34.519 --> 06:36.437
I did have an illustrator

06:36.437 --> 06:39.190
