if you're open.

06:40.316 --> 06:43.194
His name is Mr. McGooch.

06:43.194 --> 06:44.278
Stop.

06:44.654 --> 06:46.781
- Really?!
- The journey of your character:

06:46.781 --> 06:49.367
is she a squid or a squirrel?

06:49.617 --> 06:51.661
And then, in the end,
of course, you reveal...

06:51.661 --> 06:53.621
she's neither. She's...

06:53.621 --> 06:56.374
she's complicated,
like the best characters are.

06:56.374 --> 06:58.334
Yes! See, I,
I knew you would get it.

06:58.334 --> 07:02.672
