maybe, a little... gross?

07:03.381 --> 07:05.591
Tentacles all over her body.

07:05.883 --> 07:07.051
She's a monster?

07:07.051 --> 07:10.805
Oh, well, y-y--
Uh, yes, uh, but-- and no.

07:10.805 --> 07:13.099
She-- The--
See, she feels like a monster

07:13.099 --> 07:14.767
because she's different,
you know?

07:14.767 --> 07:17.437
But, but I, I think she
could be adorable.

07:19.063 --> 07:21.232
I don't mean to be immodest,
but even with my talent,

07:21.232 --> 07:24.444
I have no idea how to make
the grotesque mutant

07:24.444 --> 07:27.155
you have written,
in any way, adorable.

07:29.073 --> 07:30.950
You just said
the best characters

07:30.950 --> 07:32.660
were the complicated ones.

07:33.202 --> 07:36.164
Well, there's complicated
and there's hideous.

07:36.164 --> 07:37.790
