07:38.166 --> 07:39.834
Look at <i>The Giving Tree.</i>

07:39.834 --> 07:41.461
Despicable person.

07:41.961 --> 07:44.172
Very handsome young man.

07:45.006 --> 07:46.382
These are the realities.

07:46.924 --> 07:51.554
