about the whole squid business

07:51.554 --> 07:55.141
and we give our squirrel
some freckles,

07:56.142 --> 07:58.186
and a ponytail,

07:59.854 --> 08:02.106
some cute bangs.

08:02.565 --> 08:07.111
And, um, w-what, what happens
if I don't wanna change it?

08:09.780 --> 08:11.407
Your prerogative entirely.

08:12.033 --> 08:14.660
