have a decision.

08:29.675 --> 08:30.760
Jimenez.

08:33.054 --> 08:35.640
- Oh, Mr. Waltham.
We need to talk.

08:36.182 --> 08:37.266
Is everything okay?

08:37.266 --> 08:38.392
