cattle feed IPO road show.

09:35.575 --> 09:37.410
Well, now he just wants
to meet with me

09:37.410 --> 09:38.494
first thing tomorrow morning.

09:39.203 --> 09:40.454
He's gonna know it was me, Kevin.

09:40.454 --> 09:41.539
