10:05.521 --> 10:07.356
Well, why would I? The point is,

10:07.356 --> 10:09.317
we could both lose
everything here.

10:09.317 --> 10:11.193
We need a united front.

10:11.193 --> 10:12.820
Yeah, okay.

10:12.820 --> 10:14.739
