11:59.677 --> 12:00.678
McGooch.

12:00.678 --> 12:02.388
It would be under his imprint.

12:04.390 --> 12:05.391
What a guy.

12:05.391 --> 12:07.768
(scoffs) Right... okay.

12:07.768 --> 12:10.438
